## Research Goals ðŸ¥…	
`What are you trying to learn from this research?` 

### Goals

`1.` **Assess the degree to which LCSPv2 meets users tracking needs, is efficient and intuitive**

### Outcome
***Determine opportunities for future iterations and improvements to LCSPv2**

### Research questions

**`1.`Identify opportunities for future iterations and improvements to LCSPv2**
**`2.`Identify any gaps in current LCSPv2 Tracking experience for users on CPRS**

## Methodology  ðŸ› ï¸
Usability testing with live prototype with fake patient data with LCS cooridnator use cases.


### Location
Currently, all clinical research for CDSC takes place remotely over MS Teams. We do not have processes in place to conduct in-person research with clinicians and VA staff. We will update this guide as things change.

