## Recruitment ðŸŽ¯	

### Recruitment approach
`Audience:` CPRS LCS Coordinators 

**`5.`Product SME shared contacts** 

### Recruitment criteria

- Primary user type - LCS Coordinators currently on CPRS EHR
Other Criteria
- Diversity in VISNs and locations
- Established vs newly launched LCS programs 
- Varying clinical models - Hybrid and Consult model of LCS 
- Coordinators with varying levels of LCS experience - ranging from Less than 1 year up to 5 years + 
- Part time and full time LCS Coordinators
- Coordinators with low and high patient caseloads

