Amber and Angela from NCLCS (ccâ€™d) believe your insights would be valuable to helping understand additional LCS contexts as we roll this tool out to more locations. Would you be willing to have a 30 minute call to explore a prototype of a new LCS platform? This is an entirely voluntary request. After an initial call, you would have the opportunity to try the LCSPv2 tool and explore if it might be a useful support for your work.   
Here is a link with some potential meeting times. If none of these work, please let me know when might be better for you. Thank you for your time!  I'd be happy to answer any questions you may have.  

Best, 
